      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Wight-Lord is the supreme commander of the undead armies besieging Svellheim's holds — an ancient warlord who died with conquest unfinished and rose with all of that ambition intact. Armored in blackened plate etched with necromantic runes, the Wight-Lord commands the battlefield with calculated precision. Its siege commander abilities coordinate undead forces across vast distances, and its multiple attack sequences make it a solo threat capable of holding multiple heroes at bay simultaneously.</p>",
